name: 6:18 Prayer Meeting
where: S'kidlettes Room

name: Sunday Service
description:
Our services start at 9:30am. We spend some time singing and praying together. We then have a short tea and coffee break while children move to age appropriate groups, Summerleas Kids and Crèche, for the teaching time. A passage from the Bible is then read and our pastor helps us engage with the passage through a sermon. After this, we sing again, before sharing morning tea together. This is a great opportunity to build community and make new friends.

We'd love for you to join us on Sunday mornings for our weekly service!
where: Tarremah School 27 Nautilus Grove, Huntingfield, Tasmania
